1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 24=

3
00:00:44,430 --> 00:00:45,270
Huaijin,

4
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:46,840
stop this now.

5
00:00:47,710 --> 00:00:48,790
Huo Linchuan,

6
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:51,000
you've been working together!

7
00:00:51,710 --> 00:00:53,070
You must die today!

8
00:00:54,110 --> 00:00:54,950
Yunzhou.

9
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:56,440
Yunzhou!

10
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,480
Yunzhou.

11
00:01:01,110 --> 00:01:02,070
Granny Liu.

12
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,280
Child,

13
00:01:06,430 --> 00:01:07,920
what happened?

14
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,230
Granny.

15
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,400
Tell us. Are you a foundling?

16
00:01:12,420 --> 00:01:13,280
No.

17
00:01:13,310 --> 00:01:14,150
Still denying it?

18
00:01:15,310 --> 00:01:16,280
Are you a foundling?

19
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,240
No.

20
00:01:18,406 --> 00:01:19,280
- Are you?
- Are you?

21
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:21,400
- Are you?
- Tell us.

22
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,710
What are you all doing here?

23
00:01:22,710 --> 00:01:23,820
- Go home!
- Run!

24
00:01:24,870 --> 00:01:26,790
Yunzhou, why are you here?

25
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,480
Hurry home.

26
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:33,600
Come on.

27
00:01:34,310 --> 00:01:35,150
Let's go.

28
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,920
Why did you come?

29
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:41,260
You're brothers.

30
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:46,230
Why must it come to this?

31
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:48,640
Everything Huo Linchuan owns today

32
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,120
should have been mine.

33
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:51,710
Am I right?

34
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:53,590
Child,

35
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,510
what are you saying?

36
00:01:58,590 --> 00:01:59,640
Huo Wenyuan

37
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:03,070
abandoned my mother and me

38
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,280
and married anew.

39
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:07,480
My mother

40
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,310
fell ill and died far from home.

41
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:12,240
I've suffered so much contempt.

42
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,120
People pointed fingers at me.

43
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,590
Did he ever once

44
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:18,470
care about how I felt,

45
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:20,080
even for a moment?

46
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,630
Foolish child,

47
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,280
you're wrong.

48
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,590
Completely wrong.

49
00:02:31,470 --> 00:02:32,310
Back then,

50
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:36,120
if you hadn't fled during the famine,

51
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,750
things wouldn't have come to this.

52
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,030
That year,

53
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:49,400
our village was raided by bandits.

54
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:53,710
Duke Huo led troops to repel them,

55
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:57,030
saving every soul in the village.

56
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:03,430
Your mother had just lost your father

57
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:06,240
and was carrying you in her womb.

58
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,280
She was all alone,

59
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,710
a frail woman with no one to turn to,

60
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,240
facing danger she could not escape.

61
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:14,750
Duke Huo,

62
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:17,360
seeing her all alone and helpless,

63
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:21,710
placed her somewhere safe in the camp

64
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,870
and took special care of her.

65
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:28,800
Duke Huo had always been proper,

66
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:31,840
never once stepping beyond the bounds.

67
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,120
Three months later,

68
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:36,240
you were born safe and sound.

69
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,710
Take this token.

70
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:39,430
Come to me if anything happens.

71
00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:41,030
When Duke Huo returned victorious,

72
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,500
he grew very fond of you.

73
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:43,286
(Huo)

74
00:03:43,297 --> 00:03:45,030
- He gave your mother the token.
- Take it.

75
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:46,560
I thank you on behalf of the child.

76
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:51,870
He promised that should hardship arise,

77
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,870
she could seek his help.

78
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:58,750
Later, your mother fell gravely ill.

79
00:03:58,750 --> 00:04:00,630
Mother, are you alright?

80
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,920
Yunzhou,

81
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,630
take this token.

82
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,080
Go...

83
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,430
(Huo)
Go to Duke Huo.

84
00:04:08,430 --> 00:04:09,270
He will...

85
00:04:09,430 --> 00:04:11,080
He'll recognize you.

86
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:14,240
Mother! Mother!

87
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,360
Eat up.

88
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,760
You should eat too.

89
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,870
Even your own child lacks milk.

90
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:27,800
Yet you still take in a stray child.

91
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,310
Mind your words.

92
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:33,600
This child is truly pitiful.

93
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,000
He's got no parents.

94
00:04:36,870 --> 00:04:39,270
So young, all alone.

95
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,270
If we don't raise him,

96
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,430
he'll have no way to survive.

97
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,760
When the village

98
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,630
suffered famine,

99
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:54,960
you didn't want

100
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:57,270
to trouble me again,

101
00:04:58,310 --> 00:04:59,150
so you went

102
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:04,630
to Duke Huo with the token alone.

103
00:05:04,830 --> 00:05:06,336
How dare you try to cling to the Duke?

104
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:07,750
You brat.

105
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:08,720
Get out of here.

106
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,000
Duke Huo, remembering old ties

107
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,270
and seeing your wit and cleverness,

108
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,720
took you in as his foster son.

109
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,610
Come.

110
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:21,270
(Huo)
He treated you closer than his son,

111
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:24,920
yet

112
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:32,190
you were never truly his son.

113
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:33,350
No.

114
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:35,040
That's not true.

115
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,320
You're lying to me.

116
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,830
Even you're lying to me.

117
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,720
All of you are lying to me!

118
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,560
It's not true.

119
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,310
It's not true!

120
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:45,070
- Yunzhou.
- I'm the true heir!

121
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:47,920
Everything he owns
should have been mine.

122
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,270
Why should he have it?

123
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:55,670
Yuan,

124
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,950
you were meant to be mine.

125
00:05:58,510 --> 00:05:59,630
Why?

126
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,830
Why does he get everything?

127
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:04,270
I am the rightful heir.

128
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,240
I'm the one who deserves it all.

129
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,080
Why?

130
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,320
Lu Huaijin,

131
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,393
everything about this is wrong.

132
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:13,160
All these years, you pinned

133
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:16,120
your blood feud on Huo Linchuan.

134
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,430
You built the grudge from your delusion.

135
00:06:19,870 --> 00:06:21,870
Duke Huo never wronged your mother.

136
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,840
Huo Linchuan

137
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:26,360
never took anything from you.

138
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:28,480
It was you.

139
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,040
You drew your own prison

140
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:33,430
and trapped yourself in empty hatred.

141
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,430
Nonsense!

142
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,240
Stop lying to me.

143
00:06:38,750 --> 00:06:40,070
No more nonsense.

144
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,240
Do you know that in this world,

145
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:44,800
the only one I can truly trust

146
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,920
is you?

147
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:49,120
I've given you all my heart.

148
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:51,720
Why would you treat me this way?

149
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:53,260
Tell me.

150
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:55,390
Was everything just a lie?

151
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,870
Was everything false?

152
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,440
Yanzhi...

153
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:21,710
Yuan...

154
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:26,070
I'm sorry.

155
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:52,950
No!

156
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:54,000
Yunzhou!

157
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,630
Yunzhou...

158
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,630
Yuan.

159
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:27,060
(Joy)

160
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,760
♪The dream shattered♪

161
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,800
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

162
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,440
♪Like a restless soul♪

163
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,880
♪How vague♪

164
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:59,800
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

165
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:02,040
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

166
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:05,440
♪Love and hate entwined♪

167
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:08,760
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

168
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:12,880
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

169
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,750
Ruoli,

170
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:16,200
we finally drank

171
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:19,670
the nuptial wine.

172
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,520
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

173
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:26,640
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

174
00:09:27,790 --> 00:09:28,630
Yanzhi,

175
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:30,630
in this lifetime,

176
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:33,100
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

177
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,840
we have finally found closure.

178
00:09:34,850 --> 00:09:38,080
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

179
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:40,370
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

180
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:41,230
Yuan,

181
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:43,320
from this day on,

182
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:48,030
nothing can tear us apart.

183
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:52,030
In this lifetime,

184
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,910
we shall surely

185
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:57,620
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

186
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:58,550
grow old together.

187
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:02,640
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

188
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:05,800
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

189
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:10,360
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

190
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:16,280
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

191
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:19,440
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

192
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:22,400
♪Sober or indulge♪

193
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:28,840
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪

194
00:10:36,460 --> 00:10:43,300
(Joy)

195
00:10:43,790 --> 00:10:45,580
♪Flowers fall♪

196
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:49,290
♪The wind brings spring
back to the branches♪

197
00:10:49,290 --> 00:10:54,140
(10th lifetime)

198
00:10:54,140 --> 00:11:00,060
(I want to grow old with you)

199
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:02,800
♪Let destiny take root♪

200
00:11:03,050 --> 00:11:04,690
♪I'll never let go♪

201
00:11:04,690 --> 00:11:07,150
♪Waiting for fate to bow down♪

202
00:11:24,190 --> 00:11:25,710
♪The dream shattered♪

203
00:11:26,070 --> 00:11:27,750
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

204
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:29,390
♪Like a restless soul♪

205
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:31,830
♪How vague♪

206
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:33,750
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

207
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:35,990
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

208
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:39,390
♪Love and hate entwined♪

209
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:42,710
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

210
00:11:43,350 --> 00:11:48,110
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

211
00:11:48,710 --> 00:11:50,230
♪When fate falls apart♪

212
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:54,190
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

213
00:11:54,910 --> 00:11:56,470
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

214
00:11:56,870 --> 00:12:00,590
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

215
00:12:01,310 --> 00:12:04,150
♪Life after life♪

216
00:12:04,630 --> 00:12:07,310
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

217
00:12:07,950 --> 00:12:12,030
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

218
00:12:12,110 --> 00:12:15,150
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

219
00:12:15,310 --> 00:12:16,710
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

220
00:12:16,710 --> 00:12:19,830
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

221
00:12:19,910 --> 00:12:21,350
♪Now shatter apart♪

222
00:12:21,470 --> 00:12:25,230
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

223
00:12:25,950 --> 00:12:28,750
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

224
00:12:29,030 --> 00:12:31,870
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

225
00:12:32,190 --> 00:12:36,590
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

226
00:12:36,830 --> 00:12:39,750
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

227
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:44,310
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

228
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:50,230
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

229
00:12:50,670 --> 00:12:53,390
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

230
00:12:53,630 --> 00:12:56,350
♪Sober or indulge♪

231
00:12:56,790 --> 00:13:02,790
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
